      <title>Signa Prime 与 Kuehne 就紧急贷款争取时间进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/signa-prime-kuehne-in-talks-on-emergency-loan-to-buy-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在债权人开会讨论其重组计划之际，Signa Prime 和物流亿万富翁 Klaus-Michael Kuehne 的控股公司正在就向这家破产的房地产公司提供生命线进行谈判。]]></description>
